{"tid":2495540,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Cube時隔3年！新女團LIGHTSUM「超正2成員」曝光　網驚：像Jennie","createTime":"2021-04-19T08:46:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T08:51:28.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e49f5366b340cded09113aa1bd2bd05baeaeb85a","tid":2495540,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:46:11.000Z","msg":"南韓娛樂公司Cube一手打造BEAST、4minute、PENTAGON、(G)I-DLE等團體，相隔3年，該公司風光宣言將再度推出新人女團LIGHTSUM，4月起動作頻頻，先是曝光女團的名稱，19日還加碼公開2位成員的廬山真面目，年僅19歲Sangah與17歲Juhyeon，都擁有甜美的外貌，其中，Juhyeon還曾參加過《The Unit》、《Dancing High》選秀節目，累積一定知名度，甫公開便引起討論。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5574/d5574383.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5574%2Fd5574383.jpg&h=5ccba391&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Juhyeon過去參加過選秀節目。（圖／翻攝自LIGHTSUM官方推特）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5574/d5574381.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5574%2Fd5574381.jpg&h=1eeea4ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲新女團LIGHTSUM的Sangah被指神似Jennie。（圖／翻攝自LIGHTSUM官方推特）<br />\n<br />\nLIGHTSUM是Cube相隔3年再推出的女團，官方19日公開2位成員的形象照片與影片，19歲Sangah紮起馬尾時，五官神似BLACKPINK的Jennie，散發出清純可愛的氣質，另外一位17歲Juhyeon則是與演員金賽綸的樣貌相仿，她當年僅15歲就站上舞台，展現出精湛的舞蹈實力，留給觀眾深刻的印象，此次以女團LIGHTSUM正式出道，也讓歌迷表示非常期待。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5574/d5574386.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5574%2Fd5574386.jpg&h=142badf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼新女團LIGHTSUM美貌出眾。（圖／翻攝自LIGHTSUM Youtube）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5574/d5574385.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5574%2Fd5574385.jpg&h=9aa4aa16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據悉，LIGHTSUM團體名意指「聚集各個小的光點照亮世界」，19日不僅曝光平面的形象照，還有一段動態的影片介紹，網友大方稱讚「動態的更美」，引起熱烈討論，至於該團成員人數、隊員資訊並未有確切的官方消息，自曝光出道消息後，官方便對於成員的個人訊息保持神秘，使得歌迷更加關注、好奇，團體預計在2021年上半年正式出道。"},{"pid":"1a3dff47eae8850b4baeb854f27766f2066bb895","tid":2495540,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:46:55.000Z","msg":"麻麻地..<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21acbb259ff698a2b454dbf25f42f553cc2a65f3","tid":2495540,"uid":320204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:48:52.000Z","msg":"似jennie咁慘...?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"032df5e202adfa9176f502851450d34f736e75ad","tid":2495540,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a3dff47eae8850b4baeb854f27766f2066bb895","tid":2495540,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:46:55.000Z","msg":"麻麻地..<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:49:36.000Z","msg":"吹到上天<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb82b76cf24c8d1469ccc8f822e7c44e299cd9ae","tid":2495540,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21acbb259ff698a2b454dbf25f42f553cc2a65f3","tid":2495540,"uid":320204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:48:52.000Z","msg":"似jennie咁慘...?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:50:13.000Z","msg":"咁就大檸樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6430a1ca364ab6c8a8dd84320c64ed075099c030","tid":2495540,"uid":11049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:51:28.000Z","msg":"初媛呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}